# API key proxy (optional).
# If running through an organization-internal proxy, set the *_BASE_URL vars
# below to the proxy endpoint. To additionally wrap API keys through a local
# helper module (e.g. one provided by your infra team), point
# PACUTE_BENCH_KEY_PROXY_MODULE at a dotted module name that exposes
# `api_key.get_api_key_for_proxy(key) -> str`. The evaluator imports it
# dynamically; if the variable is unset or the module isn't installed the key
# is used as-is.
